  <titles>
    <title as="introduced" type="short">Regulator Term Limit Act of 1996</title>
    <title as="introduced" type="official">To provide that an individual may not serve more than 2 terms as a member of any independent regulatory commission, and to authorize an individual to continue to serve as a member of an independent regulatory commission for not more than 1 year following the expiration of the term of the individual.</title>
